@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_cmhmdi(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = v2
    v2 = ((tmp * 0.77) / 0.37)
    v2 = wp.exp(((v1 + 0.10 - tmp + 0.10) * 0.80))
    v2 = wp.sin((0.07 * (tmp + 0.54 - v2 + 0.17)))
    tmp = wp.cos((wp.exp(tmp + 0.64) - (tmp + 0.89 * v2 + 0.00)))
    data[tid] = v0
